<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>心侨 - 连接心与侨的桥梁</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* 国旗渐变英雄区 */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
                #DC143C 0%, 
                #DC143C 20%, 
                #FF6B35 40%, 
                #4B0082 60%, 
                #000080 80%, 
                #191970 100%
            );
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(255,215,0,0.15) 0%, transparent 40%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* 国旗装饰条纹 */
        .flag-stripe {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, 
                #DC143C 0%, #DC143C 25%,
                #FFD700 25%, #FFD700 50%,
                #000080 50%, #000080 75%,
                #FF0000 75%, #FF0000 100%
            );
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        }

        .hero .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .hero .tagline {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #FFD700;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .scroll-indicator {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 2rem;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
            40% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-10px); }
            60% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-5px); }
        }

        /* 导航栏 */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav .logo {
            color: #FFD700;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #FFD700;
        }

        /* 通用区块样式 */
        section {
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #191970;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section .section-intro {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        /* 关于我们 */
        #about {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff, #f8f9fa);
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-text {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .about-text h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #DC143C;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .about-text p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .about-images {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .about-images img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .about-images img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* 图片展示区 */
        #gallery {
            background: #fff;
        }

        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 350px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .gallery-caption {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .gallery-caption h4 {
            color: #191970;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .gallery-caption p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* 传统文化 */
        #culture {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #fff);
        }

        .culture-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .culture-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border-top: 4px solid #DC143C;
        }

        .culture-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .culture-card .icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .culture-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #191970;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .culture-card p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* 企业介绍 */
        #companies {
            background: #fff;
        }

        .companies-framework {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .company-placeholder {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #e9ecef);
            border: 2px dashed #adb5bd;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .company-placeholder:hover {
            border-color: #191970;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #f0f0ff);
        }

        .company-placeholder .icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .company-placeholder h4 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #868e96;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .company-placeholder p {
            color: #adb5bd;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* 东南亚展望 */
        #seasia {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #191970, #000080);
            color: #fff;
        }

        #seasia h2 {
            color: #FFD700;
        }

        #seasia .section-intro {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        }

        .seasia-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .seasia-text p {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .seasia-features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .feature-box {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .feature-box h4 {
            color: #FFD700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .feature-box p {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* 成果展示 */
        #achievements {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #f0f4ff);
        }

        .achievements-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .achievement-item {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border-top: 4px solid #FFD700;
        }

        .achievement-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .achievement-number {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #DC143C;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .achievement-item h4 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #191970;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .achievement-item p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* 核心产品 */
        #products {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #f5f5f0);
        }

        .products-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .product-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border-top: 4px solid #4B0082;
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .product-card .icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .product-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #191970;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .product-card p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* 研学课程 */
        #courses {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #fff);
        }

        .course-categories {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .course-category {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border-top: 4px solid #008000;
        }

        .course-category:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .course-category .icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .course-category h4 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #191970;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .course-category p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* 联系我们 */
        #contact {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #191970, #000080);
            color: #fff;
        }

        #contact h2 {
            color: #FFD700;
        }

        #contact .section-intro {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        }

        .contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .contact-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
        }

        .contact-card .icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .contact-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #FFD700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .contact-detail {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .contact-card p {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* 页脚 */
        footer {
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        footer .flag-bar {
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, 
                #DC143C 0%, #DC143C 25%,
                #FFD700 25%, #FFD700 50%,
                #000080 50%, #000080 75%,
                #FF0000 75%, #FF0000 100%
            );
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        footer p {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* 响应式设计 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .hero .subtitle { font-size: 1.2rem; }
            .about-grid, .seasia-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .achievements-grid, .products-grid, .course-categories, .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            nav ul { gap: 1rem; }
            nav a { font-size: 0.9rem; }
        }
    </style>
    <!-- 国旗渐变切换功能 -->
    <script src="flag-transition.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- 导航栏 -->
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">心侨 Xinqiao</div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#hanyuqiao">汉语桥</a></li>
            <li><a href="#gushi">故事里</a></li>
            <li><a href="#shangdao">商道</a></li>
            <li><a href="#jiangxinzao">匠心造</a></li>
            <li><a href="#xinqiao">新·中国</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">联系我们</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- 英雄区 -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>心 侨</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">语言为桥 · 故事为媒 · 商道为基 · 匠心为魂 · 中国为梦</p>
            <p class="tagline">汉语桥 · 故事里 · 商道 · 匠心造 · 新·中国</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flag-stripe"></div>
        <div class="scroll-indicator">▼</div>
    </section>

    <!-- 汉语桥 -->    <section id="hanyuqiao">        <h2>汉语桥</h2>        <p class="section-intro">中外语言文化交流的桥梁，让语言成为连接心灵的纽带</p>                <div class="culture-grid">            <div class="culture-card">                <div class="icon">📚</div>                <h4>汉语课程</h4>                <p>系统化的汉语教学课程体系，从零基础到高级商务汉语，覆盖全年龄段学习者。线上+线下灵活学习模式。</p>            </div>            <div class="culture-card">                <div class="icon">🎉</div>                <h4>语言活动</h4>                <p>定期举办汉语角、演讲比赛、诗词朗诵等活动，营造沉浸式语言学习环境。每月两次，欢迎参与。</p>            </div>            <div class="culture-card">                <div class="icon">🌏</div>                <h4>中外交流项目</h4>                <p>搭建中外青年交流平台，促进文化对话与友谊。留学生配对、文化体验日、语言交换计划等。</p>            </div>            <div class="culture-card">                <div class="icon">📱</div>                <h4>语言学习资源</h4>                <p>在线学习平台提供视频教程、练习题、文化小知识。随时学习，反复巩固，让进步看得见。</p>            </div>        </div>    </section>    <!-- 故事里 -->    <section id="gushi">        <h2>故事里</h2>        <p class="section-intro">用故事讲中国、讲侨情，让文化在讲述中传承</p>                <div class="culture-grid">            <div class="culture-card">                <div class="icon">📖</div>                <h4>中国故事</h4>                <p>从神话传说到历史典故，用生动的方式讲述中国五千年文明中的经典故事。每周五晚更新，欢迎收听。</p>            </div>            <div class="culture-card">                <div class="icon">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</div>                <h4>侨胞故事</h4>                <p>记录东南亚侨胞的奋斗历程与思乡情怀，传承爱国爱乡、艰苦创业的精神血脉。来自真实侨胞口述。</p>            </div>            <div class="culture-card">                <div class="icon">🎭</div>                <h4>文化故事</h4>                <p>通过戏曲、舞蹈、节日习俗等载体，讲述文化背后的深层含义与传承价值。每月一个主题故事。</p>            </div>            <div class="culture-card">                <div class="icon">🎬</div>                <h4>图文/视频故事</h4>                <p>以多媒体形式呈现精彩内容，图文并茂、视频生动。让故事跨越语言障碍，传递文化温度。</p>            </div>        </div>    </section>    <!-- 商道 -->    <section id="shangdao">        <h2>商道</h2>        <p class="section-intro">侨商文化、经贸交流、诚信立业，传承商道精神</p>                <div class="products-grid">            <div class="product-card">                <div class="icon">📊</div>                <h4>侨商案例</h4>                <p>精选东南亚成功侨商创业案例，从白手起家到商业帝国的励志故事与经验总结。</p>            </div>            <div class="product-card">                <div class="icon">🤝</div>                <h4>经贸合作</h4>                <p>中东南亚双边经贸合作项目撮合，提供市场对接、商务洽谈、政策咨询一站式服务。</p>            </div>            <div class="product-card">                <div class="icon">💼</div>                <h4>商务服务</h4>                <p>涵盖工商注册、税务规划、法律合规、人才引进等全链条企业服务体系。</p>            </div>            <div class="product-card">                <div class="icon">🌟</div>                <h4>创业经验</h4>                <p>定期举办创业沙龙与导师分享会，累计分享100+实战创业经验与避坑指南。</p>            </div>            <div class="product-card">                <div class="icon">🏪</div>                <h4>行业交流</h4>                <p>按行业细分的交流合作平台，促进产业链上下游资源对接与信息共享。</p>            </div>        </div>    </section>    <!-- 匠心造 -->    <section id="jiangxinzao">        <h2>匠心造</h2>        <p class="section-intro">用心打造精品课程、文创产品、研学项目，传递匠心精神</p>                <div class="course-categories">            <div class="course-category">                <div class="icon">🎓</div>                <h4>精品课程</h4>                <p>系统化的教学课程体系，从入门到精通，由资深教师团队精心打磨每个教学环节。</p>            </div>            <div class="course-category">                <div class="icon">🎨</div>                <h4>文创产品</h4>                <p>融合传统文化元素与现代设计理念的文创衍生品，让文化触手可及。已推出茶具、文具、服饰等系列产品。</p>            </div>            <div class="course-category">                <div class="icon">🗺️</div>                <h4>研学项目</h4>                <p>深度文化体验研学之旅，涵盖中国各地文化名胜，结合实地探访与文化课堂。每季度推出不同主题线路。</p>            </div>            <div class="course-category">                <div class="icon">👥</div>                <h4>匠心团队</h4>                <p>由资深教育专家、文化学者和语言教师组成的专业教研团队，确保课程品质与教学创新。</p>            </div>            <div class="course-category">                <div class="icon">📜</div>                <h4>成果作品</h4>                <p>展示学员学习成果与师生共创作品，包括书法、绘画、作文、演讲视频等精彩集锦。</p>            </div>        </div>    </section>    <!-- 新·中国 -->    <section id="xinqiao">        <h2>新·中国</h2>        <p class="section-intro">新时代中国风貌、文化自信，展现当代中国的新面貌</p>                <div class="achievements-grid">            <div class="achievement-item">                <div class="achievement-number">🌅</div>                <h4>新时代文化</h4>                <p>展现中国特色社会主义文化的繁荣发展与创新成果</p>            </div>            <div class="achievement-item">                <div class="achievement-number">🏛️</div>                <h4>国情展示</h4>                <p>深入了解当代中国政治、经济、社会的多元化面貌</p>            </div>            <div class="achievement-item">                <div class="achievement-number">🎓</div>                <h4>青年视角</h4>                <p>新时代青年的思想火花与文化担当，展现青春力量</p>            </div>            <div class="achievement-item">                <div class="achievement-number">🏆</div>                <h4>中国成就</h4>                <p>科技、教育、体育等领域的突破性进展与国际认可</p>            </div>            <div class="achievement-item">                <div class="achievement-number">🌸</div>                <h4>文化新貌</h4>                <p>传统文化与现代文明的碰撞交融，绽放新时代光彩</p>            </div>        </div>    </section>    <!-- 联系我们 -->    <section id="contact">        <h2>联系我们</h2>        <p class="section-intro">期待与您建立联系，共同探讨文化传承与商业合作的可能</p>                <div class="contact-grid">            <div class="contact-card">                <div class="icon">📧</div>                <h4>邮件联系</h4>                <p class="contact-detail">hello@xinqiao.com</p>                <p>我们将尽快回复您的邮件</p>            </div>            <div class="contact-card">                <div class="icon">📞</div>                <h4>电话咨询</h4>                <p class="contact-detail">+86 123 4567 8900</p>                <p>工作日 9:00 - 18:00</p>            </div>            <div class="contact-card">                <div class="icon">📍</div>                <h4>地址</h4>                <p class="contact-detail">东南亚·核心城市</p>                <p>欢迎预约来访</p>            </div>        </div>    </section>
    <!-- 页脚 -->
    <footer>
        <div class="flag-bar"></div>
        <p>© 2024 心侨 Xinqiao - 连接心与侨的桥梁</p>
        <p>Connecting Hearts Across Borders</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>